works.description:
This is one of many of my original posts 

(text, but also including my photographs) that are being appropriated by  

the site "newinteriordesignstyle2010.blogspot.   This post explains some
of  
my techniques and photos of what I have done to create more detail  
interiors of my model buildings.

This post, and the general content of my blog, is focused on providing  
tips, techniques, and ideas related to the construction of my N scale
model  
train layout as well as model trains more generally.
